Here's a single self-contained HTML file that visualizes a singly linked list. Save it as something like linked_list.html and open it in a browser. It supports:

- Insert at head
- Insert at tail
- Delete by value (first occurrence)
- Search (highlights matching node)
- Visual arrows between nodes
- Handles empty list gracefully

The UI is simple and interactive. You can step through operations visually.

